Center: Centre for Photonuclear Experiments Data, Moscow State University, Russia
title: Reactions Be-9(gamma,gamma`), B-11(gamma,gamma`), and B-11(gamma,x gamma`).

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Journal of Nuclear Physics, Vol.40, p.190 (1984)

x4freetext: Energy spectra of photons from reactions
scattering cross section and the cross section of the
nuclear rahman effect on the B-11 nucleus are as well
found. The excitation functions are calculated for
the 3.37-MeV level of the B-10 nucleus and for the
1.74- and 3.59-MeV levels of the B-10 nucleus in the
reaction B-11(gamma,xgamma`). The relation between the
total  photoabsorption cross section and the cross
section of elastic scattering of photons is analyzed
by the dispersion theory methods. Conclusions are
derived concerning spins and particles of some levels
of the giant resonance. For the B-11 1p-1H
contributions in giant resonance wave function
